l emissions that cannot be eliminated. Further, the company provides turnkey project consulting and advisory services that include initial feasibility assessments, site evaluations, engineering and design, permitting and approvals, equipment procurement, construction and installation, and final commissioning for community sized rural biogas projects and utility size renewable and clean energy projects. Additionally, it is involved in the trading of goods. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is based in New Delhi, India."}}